      <h1>Access Control</h1>
      <p class="lead">Controlled entry for doors, offices, gates, and managed properties.</p>
      <div class="actions"><a class="button secondary" href="index.html">Back to Home</a><a class="button secondary" href="contact.html">Request Quote</a></div>
    </div>
